      "stem": "A triangle has a base of 10 cm and a height of 6 cm. What is its area, in square centimeters?",
      "interactionType": "numeric",
      "config": { "unit": "cm²" },
      "answer": { "type": "numeric", "value": 30 },
      "workedSolution": "Area = ½ × base × height = ½ × 10 × 6 = 30 square centimeters."
